txt.en: Many trolls and Olog-hai no longer await orders from the Captain of the Pit thanks to your timely strikes.
Defeated many trolls and Olog-hai at Dâr Mauzur.
Defeat trolls and Olog-hai at Dâr Mauzur
Dâr Mauzur is sparsely populated with many who served under Ugrukhôr before the fall of Sauron.
Trolls and Olog-hai can be found at Dâr Mauzur.\n\nYou should defeat as many trolls and Olog-hai as possible.
Creatures of war, formally under the command of the Captain of the Pit, await orders in the desolate encampment of Dâr Mauzur. Trolls and Olog-hai found here should be dealt with swiftly.
Trolls and Olog-hai can be found at Dâr Mauzur.\n\nYou should defeat as many trolls and Olog-hai as possible.
